app_details.title: Injector Origin
app_details.description: Injector Origin is more than just an injector app. Dive into our hero guides, packed with valuable tips and tricks to master every hero's abilities and strategies. Elevate your skills and enhance your gaming experience with Injector Origin now!

reviews.content: It is a great skin injector. What I want to know is if your teammates or other players can see your skin after you injected it?
reviews.replyContent: Thank you for your review! The skins you inject are only visible to you. Other players and your teammates will see the default skin. Feel free to ask if you have more questions!

Thanks for the feedback! We're glad to hear you're enjoying Injector Origin. If there's anything specific you'd like to see or improve, feel free to let us know. We're always working to enhance the experience!
